<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_07_SU_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_07_su_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y">
          <span>
            어느 문구점에서 판매 금액이 5500원인 장난감을 할인하여 3300원에 팔고, 판매 금액이 4000원인 스케치북을 할인하여 2600원에 팔고 있습니다. 두 상품의 판매 금액에 대한 할인 금액의 비율을 비교해 봅시다.
          </span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">

        <div class="input_area">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">
                두 상품의 할인 금액은 각각 얼마인가요?​
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="row">
                  <span class="f32b">장난감: </span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2200"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">원</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <span class="f32b">스케치북: </span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="1400"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">원</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="page page_1">
              <h3 lang="y">
                두 상품의 판매 금액에 대한 할인 금액의 비율은 각각 몇 ％인지 구해 보세요.
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="row">
                  <span class="f32b">장난감: </span>
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="40"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">％</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <span class="f32b">스케치북: </span>
                  <di class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="35"></math-field>
                  </di v>
                  <span class="f32b">％</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>

            <article class="page page_3">
              <h3 lang="y">
                판매 금액에 대한 할인 금액의 비율이 더 높은 상품은 무엇인지 고르세요.
              </h3>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                  <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="장난감">
                      <option></option>
                      <option value="장난감"></option>
                      <option value="스케치북"></option>
                  </select>
              </div>
              </div>
            </article>

        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
